description:
Sora and the gang go to investigate a mysterious tunnel that appears in a Skyland field. There, they meet Empress Undergu, ruler of the Undergu Empire, who overpowers Cure Sky and the others with her immense power.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: A Grown-Up Princess and the Legendary Precure
Ookina Princess to Densetsu no Precure
大きなプリンセスと伝説のプリキュア
